It's another week of celebrating your house pride as each Hogwarts house takes centre stage! Delight in brand new, specially curated Hogwarts Gift Trunks, house pride Backpack Sets, and promotions on fan-favourites such as Quidditch jumpers, notebooks, t-shirts, cosmetics and more. 

This week you can explore the specially curated Hufflepuff collection by  heading to the link in our bio:

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Wizarding World on August 07, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and outdoors.

node.text: At times, Harry Potter could be moody and sullen (understandably!) but he's also pretty witty and great at snarky retorts. How many of these Chosen One's quotes can you recall? Head to the link in our bio to find out

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Wizarding World on August 05, 2021. May be an image of 2 people.

node.text: Sirius Black was mentioned all the way back in the first book but it wasn't until Prisoner of Azkaban that we were properly introduced to him. What were your first impressions of the Marauder and how did they change over time?

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Wizarding World on August 03, 2021. May be an image of 4 people, eyeglasses and indoor.

node.text: Godric Gryffindor's house is full of fan favourites. From the litany of Weasleys, the popular Marauders and Harry Potter himself, who is your No. 1 Gryffindor?
